said your first year you were in K Company. Were you 
all, did you... serving in different companies

13:30.436 --> 13:33.359
other than K? Well I was in K for the first

13:33.860 --> 13:42.048
two years I believe. Then I was assigned to Company 
E but I still lived in Milner the third year. Fourth

13:51.438 --> 13:55.262
year I was a

13:56.828 --> 14:03.575
half junior, half senior, so I wasn't assigned to 
