Reveille and the dressing and trying to make 
Reveille formation on time to march down to the

14:31.420 --> 14:53.193
hall and tying the necktie on the run and that sort 
of thing. I presume wrapping your leggings No, at

14:57.106 --> 15:01.915
that time, we didn't have the... You didn't have 
the wrap leggings. We didn't have the wrap

