That's right. Of course, making Reveille... then 
marching to our meals and then going to classes. If

15:25.835 --> 15:36.152
it was muddy, how the old sticky soil would boil up 
on your heels and your shoes and so on. Yeah, there

15:36.172 --> 15:37.514
were no sidewalks. No sidewalks. We had gravel, 
supposedly gravel sidewalks, but, you know, in

15:38.856 --> 15:48.291
wet weather like we have down there, why? Any 
boardwalks? No, we didn't have any boardwalks

15:50.126 --> 15:53.730
that I recall. Seen a few pictures that had some 
that I think primarily they were around the

15:55.533 --> 16:00.379
professor's homes, though. Perhaps, perhaps so.

16:08.228 --> 16:10.431
What did you do for entertainment and recreation? 
Well, there really wasn't any. Of course, we

16:15.048 --> 16:22.116
played baseball in season, and we played a little 
football in season. I mean, I was not large enough

16:22.136 --> 16:38.494
to play football, and I couldn't hit well enough to 
play varsity baseball, but I could play company

16:22.136 --> 16:38.494
football and baseball and basketball. although 
we knew very little about basketball then. It was

16:41.909 --> 16:47.998
on outside courts, dirt, cinder. Where were those 
courts, do you remember? No, they were scattered

16:50.561 --> 17:01.557
around over two or three places because two 
companies would go together to form a team, like I

16:50.561 --> 17:01.557
and K companies. We had our baseball team. Would 
this be in all sports then? In all the sports, you

17:04.597 --> 17:07.542
had two companies go together to form a team. Yes, 
at that time, yes. And there really, there wasn't

17:10.246 --> 17:15.975
any particular entertainment. We'd try to get to 
go to Bryan on occasion if we could get a permit to do

17:16.075 --> 17:24.568
that. We had to get a permit in the first year or two 
that I was there, as I recall. It could be denied or

17:32.356 --> 17:39.608
it could be approved by the commandant or the 
assistant commandant. And it had to be exactly

17:40.750 --> 17:48.122
correctly done or it would be disapproved. And 
