the grounds. What was the food like? food was good,

23:20.504 --> 23:24.849
but wholesome.

23:24.910 --> 23:37.445
Not always very tasty, but it

23:24.910 --> 23:37.445
was something that I suppose they still gripe 
about. We griped about it, but it was all right. Did

